snippet.title: Bulletombe | SAGE 2024 Demo
snippet.description:
Open me/Abreme




Ok, there are both side points for this demo, the good side is the pixel art stuff and the balanced difficulty even though its a little more than expected, the bad side is this demo doesnt even have a placeholder music or sounds so yeah, besides of that its good and i understand its still on WIP.

Ok, hay puntos para ambos lados de esta demo, el lado bueno es el pixel art y la dificultad balanceada aunque hay un poco mas de lo esperado, el lado malo es que no tiene musica o sonidos placeholder pues si, ademas de eso esta bien y entiendo que sea un trabajo en progreso.
